# $File: src/gptoolkit/INSTALL

Installation guide for GridPortalToolkit 
(http://grid-portal.sourceforge.net/gptoolkit/)


+++ Requirements to run
- java jre 1.4.2+


+++ Requirements to build
- java jdk 1.4.2+
- apache ant (http://ant.apache.org/)


+++ Install

For standard distribution in dist/ directory.
$ ant

To build classes only
$ ant compile

To remove all build files (not javadoc)
$ ant clean


+++ Running

$ cd dist && ./run.sh
(toolkit.jar must be run from its directory, otherwise required

